7 SECTION 10. A NEW SECTION OF KRS CHAPTER 625 IS CREATED TO
8 READ AS FOLLOWS:
9 (1) By December 1, 2026, and annually thereafter until December 1, 2029, the
10 Administrative Office of the Courts shall collect data from each Circuit Court
11 detailing the length of time that lapses from the filing of each petition for
12 involuntary termination of parental rights until the final disposition of the case.
